pma:database.name: natures_creatures
pma:database.pma:table: CREATE TABLE `bioclass` ( `Species` varchar(45) NOT NULL, `Genus` varchar(45) NOT NULL, `Family` varchar(45) NOT NULL, `Order` varchar(45) NOT NULL, `Class` varchar(45) NOT NULL, `Phyla` varchar(45) NOT NULL, `Kingdom` varchar(45) NOT NULL, `Common_Name` varchar(45) NOT NULL, UNIQUE KEY `Genus-Species` (`Species`,`Genus`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=latin1;

CREATE TABLE `location` ( `Species` varchar(45) NOT NULL, `Genus` varchar(45) NOT NULL, `habitat` set('mountain','scrub','forest','urban','rainforest','rocky','arid','caves','desert','brush','tundra','coastal','farmland','prairie','grassland','semidesert','savannah','swamp','river','salt-water','freshwater','pond','tidal pools','NA') NOT NULL, `continent` set('sAmerica','nAmerica','asia','africa','australia','antarctica','oceans','europe') NOT NULL, UNIQUE KEY `Species` (`Species`,`Genus`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=latin1;

CREATE TABLE `traits_individual` ( `Species` varchar(45) NOT NULL, `Genus` varchar(45) NOT NULL, `diet` set('carnivore','herbivore','omnivore','insectivore','piscivore','scavenger','other') NOT NULL, `time_active` set('nocturnal','diurnal','crepuscular','variable') NOT NULL, `yearClassified` int(4) NOT NULL, `conservationStatus` set('EX','EW','CR','EN','VU','NT','LC','DD','NE','Domesticated','NA') NOT NULL, `avgLifespan(years)` float NOT NULL, `avgLength(in)` double NOT NULL, `avgHeight(in)` double NOT NULL, `avgWeight(lb)` double NOT NULL, `avgWingspan(in)` double NOT NULL, `femaleIsSmaller` tinyint(1) NOT NULL, `isMonogamous` tinyint(1) NOT NULL, `birthType` set('viviparous','ovoviviparous') NOT NULL, `aveLitterSize` int(11) NOT NULL, UNIQUE KEY `Species` (`Species`,`Genus`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=latin1;
